&G COMBAT

&WTo gain exp and become a master of The Game, you must fight monsters
and other non-player characters. To see your classes spells or skills,
type practice. Most skills and spells have help files available.

Commands to check out:
&GKILL HIT WIELD FLEE ASSIST TRACK AUTO-ASSIST WIMPY&n
#
&G COMMUNICATION COMMUNICATE

&WThere are numerous channels to talk to other players on. The following
are the known communication channels:
&C---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&GSAY GSAY SHOUT HOLLER TELL ASK WHISPER MAIL RECEIVE CHECK GOSSIP GRATS 
&C--------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
&WTo turn off a channel:
&C---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&GNOTELL NOSHOUT NOGOSSIP NOGRATZ
&C---------------------------------------------------------------------------&n
#
&G INFORMATION

&WThe following &Gcommands &Wwill help to keep you update with the game, and
also give you your player stats:
&C---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&GSCORE HELP INFO WHO NEWS TIME WEATHER WHERE CONSIDER LEVELS WIZLIST
IMMLIST CREDITS TOGGLE FLAGS WIZHELP
&C---------------------------------------------------------------------------&n
#
&G MOVEMENT

&WTo move your character around, you simply type a direction. Valid
choices are &GNORTH EAST SOUTH &Wand &GWEST&W.

Other movement based commands:
&C---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&GLOOK EXITS ENTER LEAVE SLEEP
WAKE REST SIT STAND
&C---------------------------------------------------------------------------&n
#
&G OBJECTS

&WYou can manipulate and interact with objects in many differant ways. These
are some of the more common &Gcommands &Wto do so:
&C---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&GGET DROP GRAB INVENTORY EXAMINE EAT JUNK DONATE  
TASTE SIP GIVE POUR WEAR DRINK REMOVE EQUIPMENT
&C---------------------------------------------------------------------------&n
#
&G OTHER

&WThese &Gcommands &Ware important but don't fit in anywhere special:
&C---------------------------------------------------------------------------
&GBUG IDEA QUIT SAVE BRIEF COMPACT TITLE NOSUMMON COMMANDS SOCIALS DSPLAY
&GMINE ORE GEMS SMITH IMPROVE REPAIR
&C---------------------------------------------------------------------------&n
#
